2. **Always validate inputs** - Never trust user input, always validate
3. **Use TypeScript strictly** - No any types, proper interfaces everywhere
4. **Test thoroughly** - Write tests for all critical functionality
5. **Optimize performance** - Every component should be optimized
6. **Document everything** - Code should be self-documenting and well-commented
7. **Follow the sequence** - Build in the order specified in the task sequence
8. **Maintain quality** - Never compromise on code quality or user experience

